snippet: Against the Blue Jays, Yu Darvish of the Rangers reached double figures in strikeouts for the seventh time this season but lost for the second time in three starts.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Toronto Blue Jays beat the Texas Rangers, 3-2; other baseball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Against the Blue Jays, Yu Darvish of the Rangers reached double figures in strikeouts for the seventh time this season but lost for the second time in three starts.

headline.seo: Rangers’ Darvish Finishes Empty-Handed Against Blue Jays
headline.main: Darvish Controls Mound but, After One Bad Pitch, Finishes Empty-Handed
headline.print_headline: Darvish Controls Mound but, After One Bad Pitch, Finishes Empty-Handed
